sentences.english: Aim To recognize the complicated oil and water layers in Chang 2 oil-bearing formation of Donghan area in Dingbian oilfield.
sentences.chinese: 目的研究定邊東韓地區長2油層組複雜油水層的識別。

sentences.english: Process oily water through an oily water separator.
sentences.chinese: 用油水分離器來處理含油污水。

sentences.english: High levels of drug aromatic oil can be extracted from the oil-water separator.
sentences.chinese: 可提取高含量的藥物芳香油，從油水分離器中取出。

sentences.english: A gentleman without living is pudding without suet.
sentences.chinese: 紳士一貧社洗，猶如布丁缺乏油水。

sentences.english: We want to buy Oil, Tomato Khup , Saffron, Sugar, Alcohol, Pistachio, Fish Ton Saffrons.
sentences.chinese: 我們要採購塗油水，蕃茄，番紅花，糖，酒精。

sentences.english: Some even confused the detection method of oil-water separator material with this detection method.
sentences.chinese: 甚至有人將油水分離材料的檢測方法與此混爲一談。

sentences.english: Flow measurement of oil-water two-phase flow was carried out with a Venturi meter using differential pressure method.
sentences.chinese: 利用文丘裏管基於差壓法來測量油水兩相流的流量。

sentences.english: Apply to pumping oil-water mixture with bringing emulsification as well.
sentences.chinese: 輸送油水混合物不易乳化。

sentences.english: A three-dimensional network model for oil-water two-phase flow was proposed.
sentences.chinese: 建立了油水兩相流三維網絡模擬模型。

sentences.english: All over the ship the bulkheads sweated a film of oil and water .
sentences.chinese: 船裏上上下下的艙壁到處沾着一層油水。

sentences.english: Cocurrent flow of two immiscible liquids such as oil and water in horizontal pipe is a common occurrence in the petroleum industry.
sentences.chinese: 油水兩相混合流動是石油工業中經常遇到的現象。

sentences.english: The phenomenon of adsorption of colloidal particles at interfaces between two immiscible liquids including plane and curved interfaces is reviewed.
sentences.chinese: 綜述了膠體顆粒在油水界面上的吸附行爲及其應用。

sentences.english: But the influence on interfacial shear viscosity of model oil was different.
sentences.chinese: 而對各模型油油水界面剪切粘度的影響卻不同。

sentences.english: The oil-water contact(OWC) is the deepest level of producible oil.
sentences.chinese: 油水界面是可採原油的最深部位。

sentences.english: An efficient heterodyne frequency method to measure the concentration of oil and water mixture is proposed.
sentences.chinese: 提出了一種利用差拍法測量油水濃度的有效方法。

sentences.english: The drawing up of underlying waters or oil-water contact into an oil reservoir in the shape of a cone.
sentences.chinese: 下伏的水或油水界面呈錐形向上進入油藏。
